    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A vast empty sky, an old digital camera, and a home in the clouds…</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mom has been gone for a while, and the once teeming environment has grown quiet without her careful maintenance. Equipped with a magic flute and the support of your computer friends, it’s up to you to bring abundance back to an empty sky… all on the back of a giant flying catfish!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Wide Open Sky is Running out of Catfish is a story-driven photography game which explores themes of friendship and the impermanence of time and place.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Giant Catfish!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is your catfish lonely? No problem! Soar through the sky and transform clouds into fish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/ff5dc4a95610ff0e371918f4e4cca8b7.poster.avif?t=1765222557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/ff5dc4a95610ff0e371918f4e4cca8b7.webm?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/ff5dc4a95610ff0e371918f4e4cca8b7.mp4?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take Photos!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Document your findings! Catalog dozens of unique creatures and share your discoveries with the world below!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/a81dc1d047e15ac5351cdf74f740d1c0.poster.avif?t=1765222557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/a81dc1d047e15ac5351cdf74f740d1c0.webm?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/a81dc1d047e15ac5351cdf74f740d1c0.mp4?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Surf the Web!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk with your computer friends in Dolphin Chat! Upload your work to PhotoPond! Computers can do anything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/3d85a39f2309c9a8ba02191030708846.poster.avif?t=1765222557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/3d85a39f2309c9a8ba02191030708846.webm?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/3d85a39f2309c9a8ba02191030708846.mp4?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be Curious!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets of the sky are all around you! Never stop exploring!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/78deaf4e77848482fa01a266c5c3bedd.poster.avif?t=1765222557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/78deaf4e77848482fa01a266c5c3bedd.webm?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172760/extras/78deaf4e77848482fa01a266c5c3bedd.mp4?t=1765222557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
